{
  "stem": "717.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he said to my father-- these words I'll remember if I live another 1,000 years-- he said to my father, Hershel, you know how much it hurts me that I lost [NON-ENGLISH], his son.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But I think it causes me greater pain, the fact that [NON-ENGLISH], that me-- he called me [NON-ENGLISH]-- will not have a bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I don't remember my father's answer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But of course, they were stubborn, radical socialists at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So I didn't have a bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That caused them a lot of pain.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When we stayed with our grandparents, they used to sell bread rolls and bread.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I guess he took it from a bakery and distributed it to the neighbors so he made an extra few pennies to survive.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "He smoked a lot, my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And he had asthma.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And the doctor told him not to stop smoking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Even though this probably killed him, he said it doesn't make any difference.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "This is the only pleasure he's got left in his life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And I remember him smoking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And he died very early while we were there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I think we still, when we still stayed with them, he passed away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Because I remember my parents going to the funeral.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "A funeral at that time was no big deal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "You just went there to bury them, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And the cemetery, the huge cemetery, the Lodz Jewish cemetery, which was, I think, one of the largest in Europe, was on the territory of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "It was also there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "In fact, it was in the same street where my grandparents lived, but way back further away.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "They lived Gornicza number 40, I think.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
